name: Win your new body
description:
UFO CATCHER | Win your new body
It is hard for these two ghosts to reincarnate. Will they succeed in obtaining their new bodies for their new lives?

I have always liked UFO Catcher, though I am really bad at catching what's in the machines...

Copic marker on paper, scan and adjustments in Photoshop 2242x3000 | jpg | RGB
